    <a id="course-overview" class="in-page-link"></a>

    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center">
                    <h3 class="uppercase color-primary mb40 mb-xs-24">Overview</h3>
					<p class="lead">Having seen some resounding response for CAST, our scholarship test for foundation batches, and at the back of a lot of requests, Coding Blocks is proud to introduce to you APAT, the <strong>Advanced Programs Admission (and Scholarship) Test</strong>. For the first time ever, we will be holding an admission cum scholarship test for our advanced batches - Web Development, Android Development, Machine Learning and Competitive Coding. Students will be tested on their coding and algorithmic skills and <strong>scholarships worth up to 75% will be on offer</strong>.</p>
					<p>
						Please note that appearing for the test is COMPLETELY FREE OF COST. 
					</p>
					<div class="condensed-paragraphs mb64">
						<p>
							<strong>When?</strong> Sunday, January 14 (03:00 PM to 04:00 PM)
						</p>
						<p>
							<strong>Where?</strong> <a href="https://hack.codingblocks.com">Hacker Blocks</a> (Online)
						</p>
						<p>
							<strong>Syllabus?</strong> Algorithms &amp; Basic Coding
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mt40">
						<a class="btn btn-lg btn-filled uppercase" href="#apat-registration-form">Register Now</a>
					</div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>


    </section>



    <!-- SECTION: Course FAQ -->
    <a id="course-faq" class="in-page-link" data-scroll-id="course-faq"></a>
    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
                    <h4 class="mb16">FAQ</h4>
                    <p class="lead mb64">(Drop a line at admissions@codingblocks.com if you have further queries)</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
                    <ul class="accordion accordion-2 one-open">
                        <li>
                            <div class="title">
                                <h4 class="inline-block mb0">What is the registration fees for APAT?</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>APAT is completely free of cost for everyone.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="title">
                                <h4 class="inline-block mb0">What courses is the APAT scholarship applicable for?</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>It is applicable for our advanced batches - Web Development, Android Development, Machine Learning, Advanced Data Strictures using C++/Java and Competitive Coding.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
						<li>
							<div class="title">
								<h4 class="inline-block mb0">I have already enrolled for a January batch of one of the advanced courses. Will I still be eligible for the scholarship?</h4>
							</div>
							<div class="content">
								<p>Yes, you can still get the scholarship. We will evaluate your performance in APAT, and scholarship will be granted.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
